<P>
   GOVS-RACES (Atlanta) _ With governor's races in 36 states,
including each of the eight largest, this year's campaigns will
determine whether the Republican Party maintains the remarkable
hegemony it has gained in statehouses over the last four years. By
Kevin Sack.
</P>
