<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-06 13:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1794 &Cx1f; tab-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GOODBYE-MIZRAHI-NYTSF     10-06 2427
