province of Kosovo and then returns to Belgrade for more talks with
Yugoslav President Milosevic. By Jane Perlez.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-RUSSIA (Moscow) _ Kosovo and the Primakov Effect:
Reflecting a harsher line under its new prime minister, Russia vows
to veto any U.N. plan for military action in Kosovo. By Celestine
Bohlen.
