<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    BARBADOS: DELIGHTFULLY SIMPLE AND EFFICIENT, BUT NO MCDONALD'S?
 &HT;    With photo mug of Emling in the International folder on the Cox
