   &UR; BUSINESS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ``FASHION AND CULTURE: AN ARTFUL COMBINATION ADDS A MARKETING
SPIN.'' From WWD. Designers have long drawn inspiration from
artists _ think of Yves Saint Laurent's Mondrian dress, Stephen
Sprouse's Pop Art prints and Karl Lagerfeld's Watteau collections.
Now, however, the relationship between art and fashion has been
moving into the realm of marketing. In recent years, the fashion
industry has embraced art with the fervor of Armand Hammer and the
beneficence of the Medicis. A report.
