Tuesday with blue chips rallying on hopes of global interest rate
cuts, while corporate earnings worries sent big-name technology
shares lower for the second straight session. By Kenneth N. Gilpin.
</P>
<P>
   FRANCE-IBM (Frankfurt, Germany) _ IBM and France Telecom will
