<P>
   Scoop-o-rama!
</P>
<P>
   What follows are exclusive excerpts from my parody of the Linda
Tripp-Monica Lewinsky tapes. (Words considered too profane and
names of some third parties have been inked out. The word
``REDACTED'' is used as a substitute. ``Redacted'' is the
``expletive deleted'' of the 1990s!)
</P>
<P>
   Before you dive in, a warning. Some of the following passages
are explosive, shocking and deeply, deeply, deeply deep.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Hello?
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Hi, is this Monica?
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Mom?
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: No, it's Linda.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Linda (REDACTED) from yoga class?
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: No, it's-
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Linda (REDACTED) from Beverly Hills? My old history
teacher?
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: No, no, it's-
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Look, whoever you are, I don't even know your husband
and I've never laid a hand on him, so don't bother me again!
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Monica _ it's Linda Tripp. From, you know, the Pentagon.
From work?
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Oh! Linda Tripp. Oh my God, Linda, I have to tell you
something. You'll never guess who I'm (REDACTED)!
</P>
<P>
   &UR; -0- &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Next Day:
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Monica, do you know what it means when the president is
impeached?
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Does it have anything to do with (REDACTED) and a box
of Altoids?
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: No. It means the president can be removed from office for
``high crimes and misdemeanors.'' Are you listening to me?
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Oh my God, put on MTV right now, they're doing a
special on ``Good Will Hunting.'' Matt Damon is so cute, what's he
doing with that stupid (REDACTED) Minnie Driver! She has a face
like a (REDACTED) frying pan!
</P>
<P>
   (Note: Mr. Damon and Ms. Driver were seeing each other at the
time. They have since split up. Mr. Damon is currently involved
with Ms. Winona Ryder, while Ms. Driver has allegedly worked her
way through a couple of rock stars.)
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Monica, I'm trying to help you here. Do you know what
subornation of perjury is?
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: No, but I know what a (REDACTED REDACTED REDACTED) is!
The Big Kahuna showed me! Hold on, I have another call...My pizza's
here, I gotta go.
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Call me later.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: I will.
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Subornation of perjury, Monica, look it up!
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: OK, OK. God I hate that (REDACTED) Minnie Driver.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; -0- &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Next Day.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: I am so majorly bummed.
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Why are you upset? Is it because the president of the
United States, Bill Clinton, asked you, Monica Lewinsky, to lie
about your illicit affair?
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: No, silly! I'm bummed because I am having such a bad
hair day.
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Oh for God's sake. Why don't you just wear a beret, it's
not like you're going to be on TV or the cover of Time magazine or
anything.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Great idea!
</P>
<P>
   &UR; -0- &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Next Day.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Do you think Shout would work on a stain like that?
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Don't even try it! Don't even think about it! Here's what
you do _ put it in that plastic bag I gave you.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Oh right, the one marked ``EVIDENCE.'' Why does it say
that?
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: That's the name of a French designer, don't worry about
it.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; -0- &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Next Day.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: ... And the funny thing is, that George guy, what's
his name, George Snuggle-up-a-lot, was right outside, pounding on
the door!
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Oh my God.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: Finally the Big Enchilada opened the door like two
inches, handed him some money and told him to run down to Starbucks
and get him a cafe latte.
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Oh my God.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: It was so funny! Then I (REDACTED) him in the
(REDACTED) and he said, ``Hillary hasn't done that in 25 years.''
He's so cute. You don't think he'll make us live in, like,
Arkansas, do you?
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: Oh my God.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; -0- &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Next Day.
</P>
<P>
   LEWINSKY: I think he's going to make me ambassador to Poland!
</P>
<P>
   TRIPP: You're such an idiot.
</P>
