corporate stability and might. It is no longer enough. On Tuesday,
for the first time since the AT&AMP;T Corp. was founded in 1885, the
company introduced a brand that does not mention AT&AMP;T: the Lucky
Dog Phone Co. Television advertisements for the ``new'' company
began running on Tuesday in 18 big markets, including New York and
Los Angeles. Just as the advertisements for Red Dog beer do not
mention the Miller Brewing Co., which makes it, and those for the
10-10-321 phone service do not mention MCI Worldcom Inc., which
