   1998 Postseason 0-0 0.00 0.0 0 0
</P>
<P>
   1998 16-11 3.55 210.1 60 165
</P>
<P>
   BULLPEN
</P>
<P>
   Atlanta relievers have now gone three postseason series without
allowing a run, a string of 17 innings. They were remarkable
effective against the Padres this season with a 1.37 ERA in 19 2/3
innings. At the same time, San Diego's vaunted bullpen accumulated
a 4.64 ERA against the Braves.
</P>
<P>
   Ligtenberg/W-L/ERA/SV/BB/KO
</P>
