   FIRST BASE
</P>
<P>
   Wally Joynrer/Jim Leyrtiz
</P>
<P>
   Wally Joyner gets the start. But the 36-year-old Joyner is
getting daily treatment for a shoulder injury, while Leyritz is
already being dubbed Mr. October Jr. for his postseason power
works. Leyritz, the Yankees castoff whose dramatic three-run blast
off Mark Wohlers in Game 4 of the 1996 World Series, tied a game in
the Houston series and won another with home runs. Leyritz and
Joyner could be in the lineup together, with Leyrtiz behind the
plate _ particularly for Sterling Hitchcock in Game 3.
</P>
