   THIRD BASE: Ken Caminiti
</P>
<P>
   Hello, Mr. Caminiti? To make something of the series, the Padres
have to juice up their offense, and Caminiti needs to play a big
role. The concern is he slumped to .177 in September and then was a
non-factor in the Houston series with two singles. He was the
league MVP two years ago, but he's had shoulder surgery and his
numbers are down. Still, a rugged competitor.
</P>
