available to pinch hit or as a late-inning defensive sub at first
base. Ruben Rivera could get a start in center against Tom Glavine.
Mark Sweeney and John Vander Wal, a late season pickup are
left-handed bats off the bench _ with Vander Wal saved for key
late-game situations.
