</P>
<P>
   The only lefty starter the Braves will face. It might figure to
be a mismatch opposite Greg Maddux, but Hitchcock threw one of the
games of his life for the Padres to get here, taking on Randy
Johnson in the decisive Game 4 and coming out with a 6-1 victory.
Posted a career-best 3.93 ERA this past season. He works with
ex-Yankee teammate Jim Leyritz, who claims Hitchcock's downfall has
been a lack of confidence to throw strikes and thus getting behind
in the count.
