<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-06 22:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2918 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HUNNEMAN-NRT-BOS &LR;      10-06 0724
